(17, 2979, 'Considerationes sobre la Fertilizacion del arroz en produccion ecologica e\r\nintegrada en las marismas del Guadalquivir', 'es', 'Considerationes on fertilization of rice in organic production and\r\nintegrated in the marshes of the Guadalquivir', 'en', 'Considerations on the fertilization of rice in organic and integrated production in the marshes of Guadalquivir', 23, 6, 2, '2013-07-02', NULL),
(18, 2979, 'En nuestros ensayos sobre producción ecológica, la variedad Bomba, de grano redondo y alta calidad culinaria, se alcanzaron óptimos rendimientos en grano (4256 kg/ha) con dosis de 2000 kg/ha de abonado en forma órgano-mineral (permitido para este tipo de producción), lo que solamente supuso, por hectárea, 70 unidades de nitrógeno y 80 unidades de anhídrido fosfórico.', 'es', 'In our tests on organic production, variety pump, round grain and high culinary quality, reached optimum yields in grain (4256 kg / has) with doses of 2000 kg / has of paid in the form organo-mineral (permitted for this type of production), which only meant, per hectare, nitrogen 70 units and 80 units of phosphoric anhydride.', 'en', 'In our tests on organic production, variety pump, round grain and high culinary quality, reached optimum yields in grain (4256 kg / has) with doses of 2000 kg / which were provided in the form organo-mineral (permitted for this type of production), which only meant, per hectare, 70 units of nitrogen and 80 units of phosphoric anhydride.', 23, 8, 2, '2013-07-02', NULL),
