(54, 2990, 'Haciendo uso de conocimientos etnoedafológicos y etnoagronómicos de diversas regiones del mundo, se demostrará como el ser humano es capaz de conseguir una agricultura sustentable en condiciones ambientales inverosímiles. La degradación o pérdida del suelo deviene de la aplicación de unos conocimientos derivados de modelos culturales-productivos que si resultan ser insostenibles.', 'es', 'Making use of knowledge etnoedafologicos and etnoagronomicos from different regions of the world, it will show as the human being is able to get a sustainable agriculture in unlikely environmental conditions. Degradation or loss of soil is the application of knowledge derived from culturales-productivos models that if you prove to be unsustainable.', 'en', 'Making use of knowledge related to soils and agriculture from different regions of the world, it will show that humans are able to get a sustainable agriculture in unlikely environmental conditions. Degradation or loss of soil is the application of knowledge derived from production models that have proven to be unsustainable. ', 23, 8, 2, '2013-07-02', NULL),
