(65, 2991, 'Por todo ello, y con el fin de conocer los efectos del cultivo del maíz transgénico sobre algunos de los habitantes de la rizósfera, se diseñó un trabajo de investigación en condiciones controladas, con el objetivo de evaluar las consecuencias de cultivos sucesivos de maíz modificado genéticamente sobre la actividad microbiológica del suelo. En este estudio, se comparo la evolución de las poblaciones microbianas de la rizósfera plantas de maíz transgénico, inoculadas previamente con hongos MA, con las desarrolladas por plantas de maíz de variedades locales o híbridas cultivadas en las mismas condiciones.', 'es', 'For all these reasons, and in order to know the effects of the cultivation of transgenic maize on some of the inhabitants of the rhizosphere, was designed a research work in controlled conditions, with the objective of evaluating the consequences of successive crops of genetically modified maize on soil microbiological activity. In this study, is compare the evolution of microbial populations in the rhizosphere of transgenic maize plants previously inoculated with fungi MA, with those developed by corn plants of local or hybrid varieties grown under the same conditions.', 'en', 'In order to know the effects of the cultivation of transgenic maize on some of the inhabitants of the rhizosphere, a research work was designed in controlled conditions, with the objective of evaluating the consequences of successive crops of genetically modified maize on soil microbiological activity. In this study, the evolution of microbial populations in the rhizosphere of transgenic maize plants previously inoculated with fungi MA  is compared  with those developed by corn plants of local or hybrid varieties grown under the same conditions.', 23, 8, 2, '2013-07-02', NULL),
