(69, 2995, 'Transferencia tecnologica del compostaje de alperujo en Andalucia', 'es', 'Technology transfer of the composting of alperujo in Andalusia', 'en', 'Technology transfer of the alperujo composting in Andalusia', 23, 6, 2, '2013-07-02', NULL),
(70, 2995, 'En este trabajo se indican las actividades de transferencia tecnológica que la Administración Andaluza está llevando a cabo desde 2002 para potenciar y extender el compostaje del alperujo. También se describe la metodología empleada para la producción industrial del compost y los beneficios observados en el suelo tras su aplicación en el olivar. La transferencia tecnológica se centra en el asesoramiento sobre el dimensionamiento de las plantas de compostaje, elección del sistema más adecuado y estudio de viabilidad económica, y el cálculo de la mezcla idónea de subproductos orgánicos a ser co-compostados. Además se han elaborado documentos técnicos descargables desde la web, se celebran jornadas técnicas y visitas a instalaciones en marcha. En cuanto al apoyo financiero, se realizan convocatorias anuales de subvenciones para la construcción de las plantas y adquisición de maquinaria y equipos. Estas actividades han derivado en la creación de un Grupo de Trabajo de intercambio\r\nde experiencias con el objetivo de transferir a los interesados la información existente en este sector. Finalmente, se potencia una retroalimentación con grupos de investigación dirigida a resolver las cuestiones de mayor interés de esta actividad.', 'es', 'This work shows the activities of technology transfer, the Andalusian administration is carried out since 2002 to enhance and extend the composting of alperujo. It also describes the methodology employed for the production of compost and the benefits observed in the soil after application in the olive grove. Technology transfer focuses on advice on the dimensioning of the plants of composting, choice of the most suitable system and study of economic viability, and the calculation of the ideal mixture of organic by-products to be co-composted. Also downloadable from the web technical documents were drafted, technical seminars and visits to facilities are held up. In terms of financial support, there are annual calls for subsidies for the construction of the plants and acquisition of machinery and equipment. These activities have resulted in the creation of a working group of Exchange\r\nexperiences with the aim of transferring existing data on this sector stakeholders. Finally, power feedback with research groups aimed at resolving the issues of greatest interest of this activity.', 'en', 'This work shows the activities of technology transfer that the Andalusian administration carried out since 2002 to enhance and extend the composting of alperujo. It also describes the methodology employed for the production of compost and the benefits observed in the soil after application in the olive grove. Technology transfer focuses on providing advice on the dimensioning of the plants of composting, selection of the most suitable system and study of economic viability, and the calculation of the ideal mixture of organic by-products to be co-composted. In addition, technical documents were drafted downloadable from the web, and technical seminars and visits to facilities were held up. In terms of financial support, there are annual calls for subsidies for the construction of the plants and acquisition of machinery and equipment. These activities have resulted in the creation of a working group of experiences'' exchanging with the aim of transferring existing data on this sector stakeholders. Finally, feedback from research groups aimed at resolving the issues of greatest interest of this activity was received.', 23, 8, 2, '2013-07-02', NULL),
