(219, 3247, 'Transferencia tecnológica del compostaje de alperujo en Andalucía', 'es', 'Technology transfer from the composting of alperujo in Andalusia', 'en', 'Technology transfer from the composting of alperujo in Andalusia', 23, 6, 2, '2013-11-04', NULL),
(220, 3247, 'El compostaje de subproductos agrarios para su posterior aplicación en suelos con manejo ecológico constituye una tendencia creciente en Andalucía. Desde 2002, se está transfiriendo la tecnología del compostaje de alperujos, producida desde los grupos de investigación a las agroindustrias interesadas, gracias a un asesoramiento técnico especifico. Se ha puesto en marcha, además, una línea de ayudas para la construcción de plantas de compostaje. Como consecuencia, se ha aumentado exponencialmente la producción de este tipo de compost, que retroalimenta a los grupos de investigación que investigan diversos aspectos de esta temática.', 'es', 'The composting of agricultural by-products for their subsequent application to soils with ecological management is a growing trend in Andalusia. Since 2002, is being transferred the technology of composting of alperujo, produced from research groups to concerned agro-industries, thanks to a technical advice specific. It has set up, in addition, a line of aid for the construction of composting plants. As a result, increased exponentially the production of this type of compost that feeds the research groups that investigate various aspects of this topic.', 'en', 'The composting of agricultural by-products for their subsequent application to soils with ecological management is a growing trend in Andalusia. Since 2002, the technology of composting of alperujo is being transferred, produced from research groups to concerned agro-industries, thanks to a technical-specific advice. It has set up, in addition, a line of aid for the construction of composting plants. As a result, it increased exponentially the production of this type of compost that feeds the research groups that investigate various aspects of this topic.', 23, 8, 2, '2013-11-04', NULL),
