(235, 3644, 'Los sistemas caprinos lecheros de sierra semiextensivos están muy cercanos al modelo de producción ecológica y que, para que sean rentables, es necesario comercializar sus productos como ecológicos a un precio alrededor del 30% superior al convencional y diversificar con otra actividad productiva, como puede ser el porcino ibérico.', 'es', 'Semiextensivos sierra dairy goats systems are very close to the model of ecological production and that, to make them profitable, is necessary to market its products as organically at a price around 30% more than the conventional and diversify with other productive activity, such as the Iberian pig.', 'en', 'Sierra dairy goats systems are very close to the model of ecological production and that, to make them profitable, is necessary to market its products as organically at a price around 30% more than the conventional and diversify with other productive activity, such as the Iberian pig.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-05', NULL),
