(261, 3648, 'Varroa jacobsoni es un ácaro que se convirtió en parásito de la abeja Apis mellifera\r\ncuando ésta fue introducida en Asia para obtener mejores rendimientos, detectándose\r\nen España a mediados de la década de los ochenta.', 'es', 'Varroa jacobsoni is a mite which became parasite of the honey bee Apis mellifera\r\nWhen was this introduced in Asia for better returns, being detected\r\nin Spain in the mid-1980s.', 'en', 'Varroa jacobsoni is a mite which became parasite of the honey bee Apis mellifera\r\nwhen was this introduced in Asia for better returns, being detected in Spain in the mid-1980s.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-05', NULL),
