(318, 3656, 'Conocer el impacto de las distintas estrategias es el objetivo de este ensayo de dos años en Deifontes (Granada) que compara en un diseño en bloques al azar de tres tratamientos con cuatro repeticiones el efecto de una cubierta de veza-cebada\r\nmanejada con desbrozadora, con otra de la misma composición pero incorporada\r\nmediante cultivador, y otra de vegetación natural también incorporada, que suele ser la opción más frecuente entre olivareros ecológicos.', 'es', 'Awareness of the impact of different strategies is the goal of this two year trial in Deifontes (Granada) that compares in a block design at random from three treatments with four replicates the effect of a veza-cebada cover\r\nhandled brushcutter, with another of the same composition but incorporated\r\nthrough grower, and other natural vegetation also built-in, which tends to be the most frequent choice among olive green.', 'en', 'Awareness of the impact of different strategies is the goal of this two year trial in Deifontes (Granada) that compares in a block design at random from three treatments with four replicates the effect of a veza-cebada cover handled brushcutter, with another of the same composition but incorporated through grower, and other natural vegetation also built-in, which tends to be the most frequent choice among olive green.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-05', NULL),
