(403, 3670, 'Perspectives en agriculture biologique à l’horizon 2015', 'fr', 'Perspectives in organic agriculture by 2015', 'en', 'Perspectives in organic agriculture by 2015', 89, 6, 2, '2013-11-08', NULL),
(404, 3670, 'Cet article donne des éléments de perspective à l’horizon 2015 sur les conversions à l’AB à partir du recensement agricole 2010. D’après les intentions de conversion recueillies, près de 18 600 exploitations pourraient se convertir à l’AB d’ici 2015. Si cela se confirme, plus de 7 % des exploitations agricoles françaises (à effectif constant) seraient alors en bio. Les exploitations qui se convertiraient présentent de fortes similitudes avec les exploitations déjà en AB. La conversion est, semble-t-il, envisagée surtout par des agriculteurs relativement jeunes, ayant une formation et des activités de transformation ou de valorisation de leurs produits proches des agriculteurs déjà en AB.', 'fr', 'This article gives some perspective by 2015 on conversions in the AB from the Census of Agriculture 2010. According to collected conversion intentions, near 18 600 farms could convert to the AB by 2015. If this is confirmed, more than 7% of French farms (at constant effective) would be then in bio. Farms that would convert show strong similarities with holdings already in AB. The conversion is, apparently, considered mainly by relatively young farmers, with training and activities of transformation or upgrading of their close products from farmers already in AB.', 'en', 'This article gives some perspective by 2015 on conversions in the AB from the Census of Agriculture 2010. According to collected conversion intentions, near 18 600 farms could convert to the AB by 2015. If this is confirmed, more than 7% of French farms (at constant effective) would be then in bio. Farms that would convert show strong similarities with holdings already in AB. The conversion is, apparently, considered mainly by relatively young farmers, with training and activities of transformation or upgrading of their close products from farmers already in AB.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-08', NULL),
