(514, 3691, 'Las variedades tradicionales y el conocimiento asociado a su uso y manejo en las huertas de la vega de Granada', 'es', 'Traditional varieties and the knowledge associated with their use and management in the orchards of the vega de Granada', 'en', 'Traditional varieties and the knowledge associated with their use and management in the orchards of the Vega de Granada', 89, 6, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
(515, 3691, 'La biodiversidad cultivada juega un papel fundamental en los agroecosistemas ya que participa en el desarrollo de propiedades emergentes, tales como la estabilidad y la sustentabilidad. Esta diversidad tiene un significado biológico y cultural, puesto que está íntimamente unida al conocimiento campesino que se halla en la base del desarrollo de los distintos agroecosistemas.', 'es', 'Cultivated biodiversity plays a critical role in ecosystems as it participates in the development of emergent properties, such as the stability and sustainability. This diversity has a meaning biological and cultural, since it is closely attached to peasant knowledge which is based on the development of different agroecosystems.', 'en', 'Cultivated biodiversity plays a critical role in ecosystems as it participates in the development of emergent properties, such as the stability and sustainability. This diversity has a meaning biological and cultural, since it is closely attached to peasant knowledge which is based on the development of different agroecosystems.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
