(521, 3692, 'La agricultura ecológica en la política de desarrollo rural de la C. Madrid', 'es', 'Organic farming in the Madrid C. rural development policy', 'en', 'Organic farming in rural development policy from the C. Madrid', 89, 6, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
(522, 3692, 'Esta ponencia se apoya en una investigación realizada recientemente en la\r\nComunidad de Madrid, en ella presentaremos la evolución de la agricultura ecológica en esta región y mostraremos que si bien su evolución es fruto de la incorporación de este sistema productivo en las medidas agroambientales de la PAC, desde la política de desarrollo rural no se ha apostado suficientemente por esta agricultura, a pesar de darse unas buenas condiciones de mercado.', 'es', 'This paper is based on an investigation carried out recently in the\r\nCommunity of Madrid, in it we will present the evolution of organic farming in this region and we will show that while its evolution is the result of the incorporation of this production system in the agri-environmental measures of the CAP, from the rural development policy not be has bet enough by this agriculture, despite giving good market conditions.', 'en', 'This paper is based on an investigation carried out recently in the\r\nCommunity of Madrid. It will present the evolution of organic farming in this region and show that while its performance is the result of the incorporation of this production system in agri-environmental measures of the PAC, the rural development policy has not sufficiently invested this agriculture , although given good market conditions.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
