(542, 3697, 'Los policultivos en la agricultura tradicional de la Vega De Granada', 'es', 'Polyculture in the traditional agriculture of the Vega De Granada', 'en', 'Polyculture in the traditional agriculture of the Vega de Granada', 89, 6, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
(543, 3697, 'Esta investigación ha tenido como objetivo recuperar el conocimiento de los\r\npolicultivos practicados en la Vega granadina a partir de los años 30 del siglo XX. Se han realizado entrevistas abierta-semidirigidas a agricultores de edad avanzada, obteniéndose la información primaria que, junto con la observación participante derivada de las visitas a las huertas, sirvió para la elaboración de los resultados.', 'es', 'This research has been aimed at recovering the knowledge of the\r\npolyculture in the plain of Granada from the thirties of the twentieth century. Interviews abierta-semidirigidas elderly farmers, resulting in the primary information which, together with the participant observation for visits to orchards, served for the preparation of the results have been.', 'en', 'This research has been aimed at recovering the knowledge of the\r\npolyculture in the plain of Granada from the thirties of the twentieth century. Interviews have been conducted semi-structured open-aged farmers, obtaining primary information, along with participant observation derived from visits to the gardens, served for the processing of the results.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
