(551, 3698, 'La biofumigación and solarización es una técnica utilizada en Agricultura Ecológica para la desinfección de suelos en cultivos bajo invernadero. Dicha práctica ha mostrado ser eficaz en el control de patógenos, además de tener un efecto beneficioso sobre la fertilidad del suelo.', 'es', 'Biofumigation and solarization is a technique used in organic farming for crops under greenhouse soil disinfection. The practice has shown to be effective in the control of pathogens, as well as having a beneficial effect on the fertility of the soil.', 'en', 'Biofumigation and solarization is a technique used in organic farming for crops under greenhouse soil disinfection. The practice has shown to be effective in the control of pathogens, as well as having a beneficial effect on the fertility of the soil.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-12', NULL),
