(602, 3705, 'Se estudia la influencia de la fertilización en la calidad de la producción en una parcela de ciruelo en cultivo ecológico (variedad Santa Rosa sobre pie Marianna GF 8-1). Los tratamientos ensayados durante dos campañas han sido siete; aplicaciones anual y bianual de dos tipos de fertilización orgánica (un compost comercial procedente de estiércol de oveja y un abono verde compuesto de una mezcla de gramínea y leguminosa) y un biofertilizante (un preparado comercial a base de las bacterias Azospirillum brasilense y Pantoea dispersa). Así mismo se dispone un testigo sin aporte fertilizante alguno.', 'es', 'We have studied the influence of fertilization on the quality of production in a plot of plum in organic farming (variety Santa Rosa on foot Marianna GF 8-1). The treatments tested during two campaigns have been seven; applications annual and biannual two types of Organic fertilization (a compost commercial sheep manure and green manure composed of a mixture of grass and legume) and a bio (a commercial preparation based on bacteria Azospirillum brasilense and dispersed Pantoea). Likewise a witness without fertilizer input is available one.', 'en', 'We have studied the influence of fertilization on the quality of production in a plot of plum in organic farming (variety Santa Rosa on foot Marianna GF 8-1). The treatments tested during two campaigns were seven; annual and biannual applicationsof two types of Organic fertilizer (a compost commercial sheep manure and green manure composed of a mixture of grass and legume) and a biofertilizer (a commercial preparation based on bacteria Azospirillum brasilense and dispersed Pantoea).  It also provides a control without any fertilizer input.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
