(630, 3709, 'En este estudio se determinan las potencialidades y limitantes para el desarrollo de la ganadería ecológica en el Parque Natural, se caracterizan los sistemas ganaderos ecológicos de su área de influencia y se plantean estrategias de mejora.', 'es', 'This study identifies the potential and constraints for the development of ecological farming in the Natural Park, ecological livestock systems in its area of influence are characterized and arise improvement strategies.', 'en', 'In this study identifies the potential and constraints for the development of organic farming in the Natural Park are characterized organic livestock systems in their area of ​​influence and suggest strategies for improvement.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
