(636, 3710, 'De la idea al mercado: perspectivas para las variedades locales de hortícolas en función de su demanda por los consumidores', 'es', 'From the idea to the market: prospects for the local varieties of vegetables depending on your demand by consumers', 'en', 'From the idea to the market: prospects for the local varieties of vegetables depending on your demand by consumers', 89, 6, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
(637, 3710, 'Las iniciativas de conservación de variedades locales y de la diversidad de las plantas cultivadas han aparecido estos últimos años en el paisaje asociativo europeo. Estas asociaciones, que se mueven con pocos medios, defienden la biodiversidad cultivada, una dimensión olvidada en el desarrollo agrícola del siglo XX.', 'es', 'Conservation of local varieties and the diversity of cultivated plants initiatives have appeared in recent years in the European associative landscape. These associations, which move with few means, defend the cultivated biodiversity, a forgotten dimension in the agricultural development of the 20th century.', 'en', 'Conservation of local varieties and the diversity of cultivated plants initiatives have appeared in recent years in the European associative landscape. These associations, which move with few means, defend the cultivated biodiversity, a forgotten dimension in the agricultural development of the 20th century.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
