(642, 3711, 'La cebolla de fuentes de ebro: caracterización de ecotipos y mejora de la calidad', 'es', 'The onions from fuentes de ebro: characterization of ecotypes and quality improvement', 'en', 'The onions from fuentes de ebro: characterization of ecotypes and quality improvement', 89, 6, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
(643, 3711, 'En Aragón existe una cebolla autóctona denominada ‘Cebolla de Fuentes de Ebro. Estudios previos realizados con esta variedad muestran variabilidad en caracteres de interés, lo que permite contemplar la posibilidad de iniciar un programa de mejora con objeto de obtener una semilla seleccionada que produzca bulbos de mayor calidad y uniformidad. Los resultados que se obtengan de las diferentes determinaciones serán utilizados para tipificar la variedad así como para seleccionar el mejor o los mejores ecotipos que servirán de base para el programa de mejora que se pretende iniciar con esta variedad.', 'es', 'There is a so-called native onion in Aragon '' sources of Ebro of onion. Previous studies with this variety show variability in traits of interest, which allows us to contemplate the possibility of starting a program of improvement in order to obtain a selected seed that produces bulbs of higher quality and uniformity. The results to be obtained from the different determinations will be used to establish the variety as well as to select the best or the best ecotypes that will form the basis for the improvement programme that aims to start with this variety.', 'en', 'There is a so-called native onion in Aragon ''Cebolla de Fuentes de Ebro''. Previous studies with this variety show variability in traits of interest, which allows us to contemplate the possibility of starting a program of improvement in order to obtain a selected seed that produces bulbs of higher quality and uniformity. The results obtained from the different determinations will be used to establish the variety as well as to select the best or the best ecotypes that will form the basis for the improvement programme that aims to start with this variety.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
