(649, 3712, 'El presente trabajo estudia la utilización de las leguminosas forrajeras en las\r\nalternativas de cultivo en los secanos de Aragón, como fuente de provisión de nitrógeno de otras especies y para cubrir las necesidades proteínicas de la ganadería ecológica extensiva.', 'es', 'The present work studies the use of forage legumes in the\r\nchoices of cultivation in the drylands of Aragon, as a source of nitrogen for the protein needs of the organic cattle ranching and other species.', 'en', 'The present work studies the use of forage legumes in the choices of cultivation in the drylands of Aragon, as a source of nitrogen for the protein needs of the organic cattle ranching and other species.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-20', NULL),
