(769, 3729, 'En este trabajo se estudian en forma comparada y desde un punto de vista químico; diversos tipos de compost (algunos comerciales) y su posible aplicación a suelos en función de su pH. La presencia de metales pesados hace pensar que el origen de los compost comerciales no siempre procede de ganadería extensiva.', 'es', 'In this work are studied in comparative form and from a chemical point of view; different types of compost (some commercial) and its possible application to soils depending on its pH. The presence of heavy metals suggests that the origin of commercial compost does not always come from ranching.', 'en', 'This work studies in comparative form and from a chemical point of view; different types of compost (some commercial) and its possible application to soils depending on its pH. The presence of heavy metals suggests that the origin of commercial compost does not always come from ranching.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-11-21', NULL),
