(901, 3846, 'En este trabajo, realizado en el segundo año de una rotación ecológica, tras un cultivo de girasol, se implantó un cultivo de guisantes proteaginosos, con el objetivo de conocer la pérdida de rendimiento asociada a una infestación natural de arvenses y precisar el periodo crítico de tolerancia y el periodo crítico libre de malas hierbas para este cultivo. El ensayo se realizó en una finca de secano representativa de la campiña andaluza.', 'es', 'In this work, conducted in the second year of an ecological rotation after a sunflower crop, a crop of peas protein, in order to know the yield loss associated with a natural infestation of weeds and specify the critical period of tolerance and the critical period free of weeds for this crop was introduced. The trial was conducted in a dryland farm representative of the Andalusian countryside.', 'en', 'In this work, conducted in the second year of an ecological rotation after a sunflower crop, a crop of peas protein, in order to know the yield loss associated with a natural infestation of weeds and specify the critical period of tolerance and the critical period free of weeds for this crop was introduced. The trial was conducted in a dryland farm representative of the Andalusian countryside.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
