(925, 3850, 'La Red Andaluza de Semillas es una entidad sin ánimo de lucro que tiene entre sus fines hacer frente a la pérdida de biodiversidad agrícola, fomentar una agricultura de calidad, que respete el medioambiente y la cultura local y de realización de estudios que impulsen el desarrollo de la agricultura ecológica y el mantenimiento de la biodiversidad agrícola.', 'es', 'The Andalusian network of seeds is a non-profit which has among its purposes face the loss of agricultural biodiversity, promote quality, respecting the environment and the local culture and Agriculture of studies that encourage the development of organic farming and the maintenance of agricultural biodiversity.', 'en', 'The Andalusian network of seeds is a non-profit which has among its purposes face the loss of agricultural biodiversity, promote quality, respecting the environment and the local culture and Agriculture of studies that encourage the development of organic farming and the maintenance of agricultural biodiversity.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
