(968, 3857, 'En el trabajo se analizan algunas de las razones de esta situación , desde los distintos subsistemas (agronómico, social, investigación, comercial...) que constituyen el agrosistema del plátano ecológico de Canarias y se recogen pautas para potenciar su desarrollo, como son la apertura de líneas de investigación aplicada en los centros responsables, implantación de fincas experimentales o seguimiento y apoyo de las iniciativas particulares de los productores.', 'es', 'At work are some of the reasons for this situation, analyzed from different subsystems (agronomic, social, research, commercial...) that constitute the Canary ecological banana agrosystem and collected guidelines to enhance their development, such as the opening of lines of research applied to responsibility centres, establishment of experimental farms or follow-up and support of private initiatives of producers.', 'en', 'The paper discusses some of the reasons for this situation, since the subsystems (agronomic, social, research, commercial ...) that constitute the agro-ecosystem ecological Canary banana and guidelines to enhance their development are collected, such as opening lines of responsibility centers in applied, experimental farms and implementing monitoring and support of individual research initiatives producers.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
