(1034, 3867, 'Uso de semilla ecológica en la Unión Europea, España y Andalucía. Casos de estudios', 'es', 'Use of organic seed in the European Union, Spain and Andalusia. Case studies', 'en', 'Use of organic seed in the European Union, Spain and Andalusia. Case studies', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
(1035, 3867, 'Desde la salida del Reglamento 1452/2003, han tenido lugar diferentes reuniones y encuentros a nivel europeo, junto a dos estudios realizados por el Ministerio de Agricultura, Pesca y Alimentación y la Consejería de Agricultura y Pesca de la Junta de Andalucía donde se ha constatado que el uso de semilla ecológica en la Unión Europea es aún deficitario y con bastantes lagunas en lo referente a la aplicación de la normativa vigente.', 'es', 'From the exit of the regulation 1452 / 2003, have occurred in different meetings and meetings at European level, together with two studies carried out by the Ministry of agriculture, fisheries and food and the Ministry of agriculture and fisheries of the Andalusian where it has been confirmed that use of organic in the EU seed is still deficient and with enough gaps in relation to the application of the current regulations.', 'en', 'From the exit of the regulation 1452 / 2003, have occurred in different meetings and meetings at European level, together with two studies carried out by the Ministry of agriculture, fisheries and food and the Ministry of agriculture and fisheries of the Andalusian where it has been confirmed that use of organic in the EU seed is still deficient and with enough gaps in relation to the application of the current regulations.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
