(1047, 3869, 'En este trabajo, realizado en el segundo año de una rotación ecológica, tras cultivo de girasol, se implantó un cultivo de trigo blando con el objetivo de conocer la pérdida de rendimiento asociada a una infestación natural de arvenses y precisar el periodo crítico de tolerancia y el periodo critico libre de malas hierbas para este cultivo. El ensayo se realizó en una finca de secano representativa de la campiña andaluza en 2006.', 'es', 'In this work, conducted in the second year of an ecological rotation, after cultivation of sunflower, a crop of wheat in order to know the yield loss associated with a natural infestation of weeds and determine the critical period of tolerance were implanted and the period critical free weed for this crop. The trial was conducted in a dryland farm representative of the Andalusian countryside in 2006.', 'en', 'In this work, conducted in the second year of an ecological rotation, after cultivation of sunflower, a crop of wheat in order to know the yield loss associated with a natural infestation of weeds and determine the critical period of tolerance were implanted and the period critical free weed for this crop. The trial was conducted in a dryland farm representative of the Andalusian countryside in 2006.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
