(1053, 3870, 'En este trabajo se pretende comparar producciones de trigo blando obtenidas en cuatro años de cultivo y características agroalimentarias (proteína, ceniza, fibra y almidón) del grano cuando se cultivan con dos sistemas agronómicos: uno tradicional y otro ecológico.', 'es', 'This work intends to compare soft wheat productions obtained in four years of cultivation and grain (protein, ash, fibre and starch) food characteristics when grown with two agronomic systems: one traditional and other eco-friendly.', 'en', 'This work intends to compare soft wheat productions obtained in four years of cultivation and grain (protein, ash, fibre and starch) food characteristics when grown with two agronomic systems: one traditional and other eco-friendly.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
