(1066, 3872, 'Este trabajo esta enmarcado dentro de una lineade agricultura de precision y ecologica, pues se persigueuna utilizacion optima de los recursos asi como una reducciondel impacto ambiental de las practicas de escarda.', 'es', 'This work is framed within a line of precision-ecology, agriculture as is optimal persigueuna use of resources as well as an environmental impact reducciondel of the weeding practices.', 'en', 'This work is framed within a line of precision agriculture and ecological, for optimum utilization of resources as well as a reduction of the environmental impact of weed control practices pursued.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
