(1072, 3873, 'Durante la primavera de 2006 se ha llevado a cabo un estudio preliminar de la vegetación en los márgenes de los campos de una finca de secano (El Vedado Bajo del Horno, Zuera, Zaragoza). Se trata de franjas de 8 a 10 etros de anchura colindantes a campos de cultivo dejadas como orlas de vegetación para frenar la erosión que afectaba seriamente los caminos de la finca, en una zona de escasas pero torrenciales precipitaciones.', 'es', 'During the spring of 2006 a preliminary study of the vegetation has been held on the margins of the fields of a farm of rainfed (El Vedado low in the oven, Zuera, Zaragoza). It is strips of 8 to 10 out of width adjacent to cultivated fields left as fringes of vegetation to stop the erosion which seriously affected the roads of the estate, in an area of sparse but torrential rainfall.', 'en', 'During the spring of 2006 a preliminary study of the vegetation has been held on the margins of the fields of a farm of rainfed (El Vedado low in the oven, Zuera, Zaragoza). It is strips of 8 to 10 out of width adjacent to cultivated fields left as fringes of vegetation to stop the erosion which seriously affected the roads of the estate, in an area of sparse but torrential rainfall.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
