(1086, 3875, 'Resumen de comunicación vii congreso de agricultura y alimentacion ecologica', 'es', 'Overview of communication vii Congress of ecological food and agriculture', 'en', 'Overview of communication vii Congress of ecological food and agriculture', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
(1087, 3875, 'La agricultura orgánica es un rubro incipiente a nivel nacional, cuyos productos se destinan principalmente a la exportación, especialmente a Europa y EEUU. Sin embargo el mercado nacional no se ha desarrollado y existe un desconocimiento general de la población respecto de este tipo de productos.', 'es', 'Organic farming is a fledgling category nationwide, whose products are mainly intended for export, especially to Europe and the US. However the national market has not developed, and there is a general lack of knowledge of the population with respect to such products.', 'en', 'Organic farming is a fledgling category nationwide, whose products are mainly intended for export, especially to Europe and the US. However the national market has not developed, and there is a general lack of knowledge of the population with respect to such products.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-02', NULL),
