(1089, 3877, 'El desarrollo de la agricultura ecológica en el parque natural de cazorla. Segura y las villas (jaén)', 'es', 'The development of organic farming in the natural park of cazorla. Segura and las villas (Jaén)', 'en', 'The development of organic farming in the natural park of cazorla. Segura and las villas (Jaén)', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
(1090, 3877, 'Este trabajo supone un acercamiento al análisis de la agricultura ecológica (A.E.) y en el desarrollo que ha experimentado en los últimos años en los Parques Naturales andaluces. Se abordará a partir del estudio de la génesis y evolución de las diferentes experiencias de producción, elaboración y difusión en torno a la A.E. en una zona como es la comarca de la Sierra de Segura, integrada dentro del Parque Natural más grande de España.', 'es', 'This work represents an approach to the analysis of the organic farming (A.E.) and in development that has experienced in recent years in Andalusia natural parks. It will address from the study of the genesis and evolution of the different experiences of production, processing and broadcasting around the A.E. in an area as it is the region of the Sierra de Segura, integrated within the Natural Park of Spain.', 'en', 'This work represents an approach to the analysis of the organic farming (A.E.) and in development that has experienced in recent years in Andalusia natural parks. It will address from the study of the genesis and evolution of the different experiences of production, processing and broadcasting around the A.E. in an area as it is the region of the Sierra de Segura, integrated within the Natural Park of Spain.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
