(1103, 3879, 'La Fundación LEIA C.D.T. está desarrollando un Sistema Integrado de Calidad, Medio Ambiente, Prevención de Riesgos Laborales y Seguridad Alimentaria (sistema patentado bajo el nombre REINGEIS: Reingeniería de Sistema de Gestión) en una empresa navarra que elabora zumo de frutas y aceite de oliva virgen extra con denominación ecológica del CNAE.', 'es', 'The Foundation LEIA C.D.T. is developing an integrated system of quality, environment, food safety and occupational risk prevention (patented under the name REINGEIS: reengineering of management system) in a Navarrese company which produces fruit juice and oil of olive green designation of the NCEA.', 'en', 'The Foundation LEIA C.D.T. is developing an integrated system of quality, environment, food safety and occupational risk prevention (patented under the name REINGEIS: reengineering of management system) in a Navarrese company which produces fruit juice and oil of olive green designation of the NCEA.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
