(1127, 3883, 'Biosolarización y biofumigación para la producción de pimiento ecológico en invernadero', 'es', 'Biosolarización and biofumigation for the production of green pepper in greenhouse', 'en', 'Biosolarización and biofumigation for the production of green pepper in greenhouse', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
(1128, 3883, 'En la Región de Murcia la superficie de invernaderos destinados al cultivo ecológico de pimiento aumenta progresivamente. La desinfección del suelo es una práctica habitual para el control de los patógenos (Phytopthora y Meloidogyne). En un invernadero experimental contaminado de Meloidogyne incognita se ha comparado la eficacia desinfectante de la biosolarización y la biofumigación reiteradamente aplicadas al mismo suelo, utilizando estiércol fresco de oveja y gallinaza como enmienda orgánica.', 'es', 'In the Region of Murcia the surface of greenhouses for the ecological cultivation of pepper increases progressively. The disinfection of the soil is a common practice for the control of pathogens (Phytopthora and Meloidogyne). In a contaminated experimental greenhouse of Meloidogyne incognita has compared the disinfectant efficacy of the biosolarización and the biofumigation repeatedly applied to the floor, using fresh manure of sheep and chicken manure as organic amendment.', 'en', 'In the Region of Murcia the surface of greenhouses for the ecological cultivation of pepper increases progressively. The disinfection of the soil is a common practice for the control of pathogens (Phytopthora and Meloidogyne). In a contaminated experimental greenhouse of Meloidogyne incognita has compared the disinfectant efficacy of the biosolarización and the biofumigation repeatedly applied to the floor, using fresh manure of sheep and chicken manure as organic amendment.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
