(1133, 3884, 'Contribución de la agricultura ecológica a la mitigación del cambio climático en comparación con la agricultura convencional', 'es', 'Contribution of organic farming to the mitigation of climate change in comparison with conventional agriculture', 'en', 'Contribution of organic farming to the mitigation of climate change in comparison with conventional agriculture', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
(1134, 3884, 'El sistema climático está determinado por un complejo sistema de variables,\r\nfundamentalmente por la emisión de combustibles fósiles y otros gases. Esto provoca un calentamiento global de la superficie de la tierra que altera los ciclos naturales de energía, produciéndose graves impactos ambientales.', 'es', 'The climate system is determined by a complex set of variables,\r\nprimarily by the emission of fossil fuels and other gases. This causes a global warming of the surface of the Earth that alters the natural cycles of energy, resulting in serious environmental impacts.', 'en', 'The climate system is determined by a complex set of variables, primarily by the emission of fossil fuels and other gases. This causes a global warming of the surface of the Earth that alters the natural cycles of energy, resulting in serious environmental impacts.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
