(1147, 3886, 'Uso de aceites en cultivos hortícolas para el control de virosis y de sus vectores', 'es', 'Use of oils in vegetable crops for the control of virus diseases and their vectors', 'en', 'Use of oils in vegetable crops for the control of virus diseases and their vectors', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
(1148, 3886, 'El poder insecticida de los aceites minerales y su efecto protector frente a virosis no ha sido plenamente aprovechado en cultivos hortícolas y herbáceos, y durante el periodo vegetativo de los cultivos leñosos. Las propiedades de uso de aceites vegetales de colza y soja, y de aceites de pescado, están siendo investigadas como alternativa a los aceites minerales menos tóxica y de origen natural.', 'es', 'Insecticide power of mineral oils and its protective effect against virus diseases not has been fully tapped in arable and vegetable crops, and the vegetative period of woody crops. The properties of use of oils, rapeseed and soy, and fish oils, are being investigated as an alternative to mineral oils less toxic and natural.', 'en', 'Insecticide power of mineral oils and its protective effect against virus diseases not has been fully tapped in arable and vegetable crops, and the vegetative period of woody crops. The properties of use of oils, rapeseed and soy, and fish oils, are being investigated as an alternative to mineral oils less toxic and natural.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
