(1154, 3887, 'Interacciones entre trichoderma pers. Y los hongos tuber melanosporum vitt. Y el contaminante de viveros sphaerosporella brunnea (alb. Y schwein.) svrček y\r\nKubička', 'es', 'Interactions between trichoderma pers. And the fungus tuber melanosporum vitt. And the pollutant nursery sphaerosporella brunnea (alb. And schwein.) svrček and\r\nKubička', 'en', 'Interactions between trichoderma pers. and the fungus tuber melanosporum vitt. and the pollutant nursery sphaerosporella brunnea (alb. And schwein.) Svrček and Kubička', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
(1155, 3887, 'En este trabajo se ha pretendido evaluar las posibilidades del empleo de hongos del género Trichoderma para controlar la aparición e incidencia de phaerosporella brunnea, comprobando además los efectos que dicho género causa sobre el establecimiento de Tuber melanosporum en las raíces de las plantas de vivero.', 'es', 'In this work we have tried to evaluate the possibilities of the use of fungi of the genus Trichoderma to control the appearance and incidence of phaerosporella brunnea, checking in addition the effects causing the gender on the establishment of Tuber melanosporum on nursery plants roots.', 'en', 'In this paper we have tried to evaluate the possibilities of the use of fungi of the genus Trichoderma to control the appearance and incidence of phaerosporella brunnea, checking in addition the effects causing the gender on the establishment of Tuber melanosporum on nursery plants roots.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
