(1169, 3889, 'La presente comunicación recoge los trabajos desarrollados aplicando técnicas de\r\nDRP (Diagnóstico Rural Participativo) con el fin de conocer la resistencia que se pueda dar por parte de los agricultores y agricultoras para el supuesto cambio a la agricultura ecológica. En la comunicación, junto a los resultados de la investigación, se analizarán las técnicas empleadas, y las dificultades encontradas al aplicarlas.', 'es', 'This communication includes the works developed by applying techniques of\r\nPRA (participatory Rural) in order to know the resistance that can be made by farmers for the so-called shift to organic farming. On the communication, together with the results of the research, the techniques used, and any difficulties encountered will be analysed applying them.', 'en', 'This communication includes the works developed by applying techniques of\r\nPRA (participatory Rural) in order to know the resistance that can be made by farmers for the so-called shift to organic farming.  In communication, together with the results of the investigation, the techniques used are discussed, and the difficulties they encountered in their implementation.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
