(1175, 3890, 'En este trabajo, se exponen los resultados de tres años (2000-03) en dos suelos con textura diferente (arcilloso y franco-arenoso) y propiedades químicas semejantes. Se estudia el efecto de una rotación de barbecho-cebada-veza enterradatrigo duro, en manejo ecológico, sobre la biomasa microbiana, su actividad respiratoria, la evolución de la materia orgánica y el nitrógeno mineral del suelo.', 'es', 'In this work, the results of three years (2000-03) are exposed in two different texture soils (clayey and sandy loam) and similar chemical properties. The effect of a rotation of barbecho-cebada - vetch hard enterradatrigo, in ecological management on microbial biomass, their respiratory activity, the evolution of the organic matter and mineral nitrogen from the soil.', 'en', 'In this paper, the results of three years (2000-03) are exposed in two different texture soils (clayey and sandy loam) and similar chemical properties. The effect of a rotation of barbecho-cebada - vetch hard enterradatrigo, in ecological management on microbial biomass, their respiratory activity, the evolution of the organic matter and mineral nitrogen from the soil.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-03', NULL),
