(1191, 3904, 'En este trabajo, se exponen los resultados de un estudio realizado entre los años 2000 y 2003 partiendo de una rotación de barbecho – cebada - veza enterrada - trigo duro, en el que se ha tenido en cuenta el efecto de diferentes manejos de fertilización en el cereal (mineral, orgánico y sin fertilización), el efecto sobre la biomasa microbiana y su actividad respiratoria, así como la evolución de la materia orgánica y el nitrógeno mineral del suelo.', 'es', 'In this work, presents the results of a study conducted between the years 2000 and 2003 on the basis of a rotation of fallow - barley - buried vetch - durum wheat, which has been taken into account the effect of different fertilization on the cereal management (mineral, organic and without fertilization), the effect on the microbial biomass and respiratory activityas well as the evolution of organic matter and mineral nitrogen from the soil.', 'en', 'In this paper, the results of a study are presented between 2000 and 2003 starting from a fallow rotation - barley - buried vetch - durum wheat, which takes into account the effect of different fertilization managements in cereal (mineral, organic and without fertilization), the effect on microbial biomass and respiratory activity as well as the evolution of organic matter and mineral soil nitrogen.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-12', NULL),
