(1250, 3913, 'El objetivo de este trabajo es determinar el potencial forrajero de la flora espontánea de las praderas naturalizadas que se encuentran en los agroecosistemas que conforman los predios de los agricultores del sector y estimar la producción, el tipo y el manejo de los estiércoles que se producen en éstos.', 'es', 'The objective of this study is to determine the forage potential of the spontaneous flora of the naturalized grasslands that occur in ecosystems that make up the grounds of the farmers in the sector and estimating production, the type and the handling of the manure produced in these.', 'en', 'The objective of this study is to determine the forage potential of the spontaneous flora of the naturalized grasslands that occur in ecosystems that make up the grounds of the farmers in the sector and estimating production, the type and the handling of the manure produced in these.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
