(1257, 3914, 'Los agroecosistemas tradicionales poseen unos valores paisajísticos, ambientales y culturales excepcionales, que han sido a menudo menospreciados por la política de conservación y la sociedad en general. Esta biodiversidad agraria generada durante siglos por generaciones de agricultores se encuentra en grave peligro de extinción.', 'es', 'Traditional agro-ecosystems possess exceptional landscape, environmental and cultural values, which have been often scorned by conservation policy and society in general. This agricultural biodiversity generated during centuries by generations of farmers is in serious danger of extinction.', 'en', 'Traditional agro-ecosystems possess exceptional landscape, environmental and cultural values, which have been often scorned by conservation policy and society in general. This agricultural biodiversity generated during centuries by generations of farmers is in serious danger of extinction.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
