(1265, 3915, 'Se presentan los resultados parciales del análisis que realizamos sobre recuperación, caracterización y conservación de solanáceas hortícolas bajo condiciones de cultivo ecológico. El estudio incluye la caracterización de 14 entradas de tomate, 14 entradas de pimiento y 4 entradas de berenjena. Se presenta una descripción detallada de los grupos reconocidos. Finalmente se destacan, por su productividad y buen comportamiento en cultivo ecológico, las siguientes variedades: “Ceheginero”, “rojo aplastado” y “ciruela”.', 'es', 'Presents the partial results of the analysis we do about recovery, characterization and conservation of solanaceous vegetables under organic farming conditions. The study includes the characterization of 14 tickets for tomato, pepper 14 inputs and 4 inputs of Eggplant. It presents a detailed description of the recognized groups. Finally stand out, by their productivity and good behavior in organic farming, the following grape varieties: ', 'en', 'Presents the partial results of the analysis about recovery, characterization and conservation of solanaceous vegetables under organic farming conditions. The study includes the characterization of 14 tickets for tomato, pepper 14 inputs and 4 inputs of Eggplant. It presents a detailed description of the recognized groups. Finally stand out, by their productivity and good behavior in organic farming, the following grape varieties: &quot;Ceheginero&quot;, &quot;Crushed red&quot;, and &quot;plum&quot;.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
