(1273, 3916, 'Se estudió la diversidad y abundancia de colémbolos de suelo en un bosque primario, un bosque secundario y un cafetal, así como su relación con algunas variables físicas, químicas y biológicas del suelo, en el Parque Nacional Tapantí, Cartago, Costa Rica, con el objetivo de encontrar su uso como bioindicadores de calidad de suelos.', 'es', 'We studied the diversity and abundance of springtails in soil in a primary forest, secondary forest, a coffee plantation and its relationship with physical, chemical and biological variables of soil, the Tapantí National Park, Cartago, Costa Rica, with the aim of finding use as bioindicators of soil quality.', 'en', 'We studied the diversity and abundance of springtails in soil in a primary forest, secondary forest, a coffee plantation and its relationship with physical, chemical and biological variables of soil, the Tapantí National Park, Cartago, Costa Rica, with the aim of finding use as bioindicators of soil quality.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
