(1309, 3921, 'En la Estación Experimental de la Fundación Cajamar, en Almería, se lleva a cabo un ensayo plurianual comparativo de distintos tipos de abonado entre los que se encuentran dos alternativas que respetan las indicaciones del Reglamento (CEE) 2092/91 de producción ecológica y su indicación en los productos agrarios y\r\nalimenticios (T1 y T2) y una tercera alternativa (T3) con abonado químico\r\nconvencional. Se ha establecido una rotación con las familias botánicas cultivadas en invernadero, en la cual se incluye el cultivo de judía sobre el que se realiza el presente trabajo.', 'es', 'In the station pilot of the Fundación Cajamar in Almería, is carried out a multiannual comparative test of different types of Subscriber which include two alternatives that respect the indications of Regulation (EEC) 2092/91 organic production and its indication on agricultural products and\r\nfood (T1 and T2) and a third alternative (T3) with chemical Subscriber\r\nconventional. A rotation is set with the botanical families grown in a greenhouse, which includes the cultivation of Jewish on which this work is carried out.', 'en', 'In the station pilot of the Fundación Cajamar in Almería, is carried out a multiannual comparative test of different types of Subscriber which include two alternatives that respect the indications of Regulation (EEC) 2092/91 organic production and its indication on agricultural products and\r\nfood (T1 and T2) and a third alternative (T3) with chemical Subscriber\r\nconventional. A rotation is set with the botanical families grown in a greenhouse, which includes the cultivation of bean on which this work is carried out.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
