(1316, 3922, 'En este trabajo se aportan los resultados obtenidos sobre la evolución del fósforo en el suelo y las extracciones de diferentes cultivos, durante 4 años (2001-04) en base a un experimento iniciado en 1992, donde se estudiaba el comportamiento de 5 rotaciones de cereales con manejo ecológico en sistema cerrado, sin aportaciones externas de nutrientes.', 'es', 'This work provides results on the evolution of the phosphorus in the soil and the extractions of different crops, for 4 years (2001-04) based on an experiment started in 1992, where he studied the behavior of 5 rotations of cereals with ecological management in closed system without external inputs of nutrients.', 'en', 'This work provides results on the evolution of the phosphorus in the soil and the extractions of different crops, for 4 years (2001-04) based on an experiment started in 1992, where it studied the behavior of 5 rotations of cereals with ecological management in closed system without external inputs of nutrients.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
