(1324, 3923, 'La superficie cultivada en los municipios pertenecientes a la Comunidad de Madrid, según el tipo de cultivo para los herbáceos son los cereales de grano, entre los que se destaca la cebada. Las tierras de cultivos están destinadas en su mayoría a la labor de secano, agrupando los cultivos herbáceos y de barbecho, siendo la distribución completamente equitativa. ', 'es', 'The acreage in the municipalities belonging to the community of Madrid, according to the type of crop to the herbaceous are grain cereals, among which stands out the barley. The crops are destined mainly to the work of dry land, gathering crops arable and fallow, being fully equitable distribution. ', 'en', 'The acreage in the municipalities belonging to the community of Madrid, according to the type of crop to the herbaceous are grain cereals, among which stands out the barley. The crops are destined mainly to the work of dry land, gathering crops arable and fallow, being fully equitable distribution. ', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-13', NULL),
