(1332, 3924, 'Las tierras labradas de Guadalajara se clasifican en dos grupos, cultivos herbáceos o leñosos que, a su vez, pueden ser, en ambos casos, de secano o regadío. Distinguiendo entre herbáceos y leñosos, los primeros se encuentran en posición preponderante, y entre la superficie la superficie cultivada destaca la fuerte presencia de los cultivos en secano sobre los de regadío.', 'es', 'The arable land of Guadalajara are classified into two groups: herbaceous or woody crops which, in turn, can be, in both cases, rainfed or irrigated land. Distinguishing between herbaceous and Woody, the first found in dominant position, and between surface acreage highlights the strong presence of crops in dry land on the irrigation.', 'en', 'The arable land of Guadalajara are classified into two groups: herbaceous or woody crops which, in turn, can be, in both cases, rainfed or irrigated land. Distinguishing between herbaceous and woody, the first found in dominant position, and between surface acreage highlights the strong presence of crops in dry land on the irrigation.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
