(1346, 3926, 'La formación universitaria en agroecología ante el espacio europeo de educación superior (eees): algunas reflexiones para el debate', 'es', 'University education in Agroecology in the European space of higher education (eees): some reflections for discussion', 'en', 'University education in Agroecology in the European space of higher education (eees): some reflections for discussion', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
(1347, 3926, 'La presente comunicación intenta aportar una serie de reflexiones sobre cómo se debería abordar la implantación de programas de estudio oficiales universitarios tendentes a mejorar claramente la formación que hoy en día reciben los técnicos y agentes que operan en el sector de la producción ecológica de alimentos. Esperamos que estas reflexiones abran un debate que permita avanzar en la dirección más adecuada. Bienvenidas serán todas las discusiones que se planteen al respecto.', 'es', 'The present communication seeks to provide a series of reflections on how it should deal with the implementation of official University study programmes aimed to clearly improve the formation today receive technicians and agents operating in the field of organic production of food. We hope that these reflections will open a debate that will allow progress in the right direction. Welcome are all discussions that arise in this regard.', 'en', 'The present communication seeks to provide a series of reflections on how it should deal with the implementation of official University study programmes aimed to clearly improve the formation today receive technicians and agents operating in the field of organic production of food. We hope that these reflections will open a debate that will allow progress in the right direction. Welcome are all discussions that arise in this regard.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
