(1351, 3927, 'El trevo: primeros antecedentes para un manejo agroecológico de un recurso local nativo como suplemento forrajero en sistemas agroforestales de uechelepún (Melipeuco, Chile)', 'es', 'The trevo: first record for an agroecological management of a native local resource as a forage supplement in agroforestry systems uechelepun (Melipeuco, Chile)', 'en', 'The trevo: first record for an agroecological management of a native local resource as a forage supplement in agroforestry systems Huechelepun (Melipeuco, Chile)', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
(1352, 3927, 'El objetivo de este trabajo es realizar un estudio que permita conocer las principales características relativas a la especie, y su manejo, por parte de los campesinos. El trabajo se realizó en conjunto con las agricultoras y agricultores colonos del sector de Huechelepún, comuna de Melipeuco, Región de la Araucanía.', 'es', 'The objective of this work is to make a study that allows to know the main characteristics relating to the species and its handling by the farmers. The work was done in conjunction with the farmers and farmers settlers in the sector of Huechelepun, town of Melipeuco, región de la Araucanía.', 'en', 'The objective of this work is to make a study that allows to know the main characteristics relating to the species and its handling by the farmers. The work was done in conjunction with the farmers and farmers settlers in the sector of Huechelepun, town of Melipeuco, región de la Araucanía.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
