(1354, 3928, 'Estudio de la actividad antagonista in vitro de bacillus subtilis frente a los hongos patógenos de fresón fusarium verticillioides y rhizoctonia solani', 'es', 'Study of in vitro antagonistic activity of bacillus subtilis against pathogenic fungi of Strawberry fusarium verticillioides and rhizoctonia solani', 'en', 'Study of antagonistic activity of bacillus subtilis against pathogenic fungi of strawberry fusarium verticillioides and rhizoctonia solani', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
(1355, 3928, 'Los estudios mostraron que las hifas de los hongos presentaban deformaciones y colapso, sugiriendo la producción de antibióticos por parte de la bacteria. A la vista de los resultados, se deberían plantear ensayos en condiciones de campo que aborden el empleo de B. subtilis dentro de programas de control integrado contra los hongos que afectan al cultivo de fresón en México.', 'es', 'The studies showed that the hyphae of fungi had deformations and collapse, suggesting production of antibiotics by the bacterium. In view of the results, you should consider trials under field conditions that address the use of B. subtilis into programmes of integrated control against fungi that affect the cultivation of strawberries in Mexico.', 'en', 'The studies showed that the hyphae of fungi had deformations and collapse, suggesting production of antibiotics by the bacterium. In view of the results, you should consider trials under field conditions that address the use of B. subtilis into programmes of integrated control against fungi that affect the cultivation of strawberries in Mexico.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
