(1369, 3930, 'El presente trabajo estudia la sintomatología externa y los daños a nivel de la ultraestructura celular ocasionados por el ozono en varias especies de hortalizas mediante la observación de tejidos vegetales al microscopio óptico, microscopio electrónico de transmisión y barrido.', 'es', 'This paper studies the external symptoms and at the level of cell ultrastructure damage caused by ozone in several species of vegetables by the observation of plant tissue to the optical microscope, microscope electronic transmission and scanning.', 'en', 'This paper studies the external symptoms and at the level of cell ultrastructure damage caused by ozone in several species of vegetables by the observation of plant tissue to the optical microscope, microscope electronic transmission and scanning.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
