(1376, 3931, 'Producción ecológica de gallos de la raza extremeña azul', 'es', 'Organic production of blue Extremadura breed bantams', 'en', 'Organic production of blue Extremadura breed bantams', 89, 6, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
(1377, 3931, 'De 2003 a 2005 se han criado lotes de pollos de la raza Extremeña Azul alimentados con piensos formulados con ingredientes procedentes de la agricultura ecológica. Se han considerado aspectos relativos a los rendimientos productivos en vivo, al coste de la alimentación, a la carga parasitaria y a las características de la canal y de la carne. Los resultados obtenidos indican que la producción ecológica de gallos de esta raza no constituye, en estos momentos, un sistema de producción de carne viable por sus elevados costes de producción pero, al menos, existe la posibilidad que tenga cabida en explotaciones avícolas de autoconsumo.', 'es', 'From 2003 to 2005, lots of Extremadura blue breed chickens fed with feed formulated with ingredients from organic farming have grown up. Aspects relating to the performance live, at the cost of feeding, the parasite load and characteristics of carcass and meat have been considered. The results obtained indicate that organic production of this breed bantams is not, currently, a production system of viable meat by high production costs, but at least, the possibility exists that take place in poultry farms for self-consumption.', 'en', 'From 2003 to 2005, lots of Extremadura blue breed chickens fed with feed formulated with ingredients from organic farming have grown up. Aspects relating to the performance live, at the cost of feeding, the parasite load and characteristics of carcass and meat have been considered. The results obtained indicate that organic production of this breed bantams is not, currently, a production system of viable meat by high production costs, but at least, the possibility exists that take place in poultry farms for self-consumption.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
