(1396, 3934, 'En este trabajo, a partir de la información recabada con una encuesta,\r\nrealizada en 2006 a un centenar de agricultores, ganaderos y elaboradores de productos ecológicos de la Región de Murcia, se analiza la estructura y tipología de las explotaciones agrarias y de transformación, describiendo sus principales características económicas y comerciales.', 'es', 'In this work, starting from data collected with a survey,\r\nmade in 2006 to hundreds of farmers, ranchers and producers of organic products from the Region of Murcia, analyzes the structure and typology of agricultural holdings and processing, describing their main characteristics, economic and commercial.', 'en', 'In this work, starting from data collected with a survey, made in 2006 to hundreds of farmers, ranchers and producers of organic products from the Region of Murcia, analyzes the structure and typology of agricultural holdings and processing, describing their main characteristics, economic and commercial.', 89, 8, 2, '2013-12-16', NULL),
