(1769, 4015, 'Este proyecto de investigación que presentamos , surge ante la necesidad de obtener datos en Castilla-La Mancha sobre la posibilidad de realizar un control ecológico de las principales plagas y enfermedades que afectan al olivar , la vid y el almendro en nuestra región, comparándolo técnica y conómicamente con el control que realiza la agricultura convencional.', 'es', 'This research project we are presenting, arises the need to obtain data in Castilla - La Mancha about the possibility of ecological control of main pests and diseases affecting the olive groves, vines and almond trees in our region, comparing it, technical and conomicamente control that performs conventional agriculture.', 'en', 'This research project we are presenting, arises the need to obtain data in Castilla - La Mancha about the possibility of ecological control of main pests and diseases affecting the olive groves, vines and almond trees in our region, comparing it, technical and conomicamente control that performs conventional agriculture.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-09', NULL),
