(1782, 4020, 'Análisis de la situación actual de la agricultura ecológica en la provincia de almería a través del perfil del agricultor ecológico: edad, motivaciones, carácter\r\nParticipativo, tipo de cultivo y superficies', 'es', 'Analysis of the current situation of organic farming in the province of almeria through the ecological farmer profile: age, motivation, character\r\nParticipatory, crops and surfaces', 'en', 'Analysis of the current situation of organic farming in the province of Almeria through the ecological farmer profile: age, motivation, character\r\nparticipatory, crops and surfaces', 89, 6, 2, '2014-01-09', NULL),
(1783, 4020, 'Se analiza la situación actual de la agricultura ecológica en la provincia de Almería, con objeto de obtener datos sobre las limitaciones y potencialidades del sector a través de la definición del perfil del agricultor ecológico, basándonos en las motivaciones para el inicio y/o conversión a esta actividad por parte de los agricultores, en sus necesidades y disponibilidad para participar en proyectos de investigación, en los tipos de cultivo y superficies de las fincas y, en su carácter asociativo.', 'es', 'We analyze the current situation of ecological agriculture in the province of Almería, in order to obtain data about the limitations and potential of the sector through the definition of the profile of the ecological farmer, based on the motivations for the home or conversion to this activity by farmers, in their needs and availability to participate in research projectscrop types and surfaces of the farms and, on its associative nature.', 'en', 'We analyze the current situation of ecological agriculture in the province of Almería, in order to obtain data about the limitations and potential of the sector through the definition of the profile of the ecological farmer, based on the motivations for the home or conversion to this activity by farmers, in their needs and availability to participate in research projects crop types and surfaces of the farms and, on its associative nature.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-09', NULL),
