(1789, 4021, 'Durante los últimos 15 años la agricultura cubana se ha reorientado de un modelo convencional intensivo a uno de sustitución de insumos químicos por biológicos. Este proceso ha sido ampliamente documentado como “un experimento de agricultura sostenible a escala nacional”.', 'es', 'During the last 15 years the Cuban agriculture has refocused a conventional model intensive one-to-one substitution of chemical inputs for biological. This process has been widely documented as ', 'en', 'During the last 15 years the Cuban agriculture has refocused a conventional model intensive one-to-one substitution of chemical inputs for biological. This process has been widely documented as &quot;an experiment in sustainable agriculture at the national level&quot;.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-09', NULL),
