(1797, 4024, 'La práctica del entarquinamiento sigue vigente con una importante refuncionalización para la producción de las hortalizas, como el caso del Valle de Zamora y otras partes de México, en donde se utiliza para controlar malezas, plagas de suelo y mejorar la fertilidad y estructura de las tierras; además la práctica del entarquinamiento recrea humedales temporales que sirven de nichos de biodiversidad, ello conlleva una interesante funcionalidad entre agricultura y medio ambiente.', 'es', 'The practice of the silt continues with a major reorganization for the production of vegetables, as the case of the Valley of Zamora and other parts of Mexico, where is used to control weeds, soil pests and improve fertility and structure of land; also the practice of the silt recreates temporary wetlands that serve niche of biodiversity, entails an interesting functionality between agriculture and environment.', 'en', 'The practice of the silt continues with a major reorganization for the production of vegetables, as the case of the Valley of Zamora and other parts of Mexico, where is used to control weeds, soil pests and improve fertility and structure of land; also the practice of the silt recreates temporary wetlands that serve niche of biodiversity, entails an interesting functionality between agriculture and environment.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-09', NULL),
