(2023, 4076, 'La certificación de productos ecológicos y del comercio justo goza de gran atención como instrumento fundamental para la introducción en los mercados globales de las cuestiones de protección ambiental e igualdad social. No obstante, la consideración de un mecanismo padrón para la evaluación de la conformidad de tales aspectos parece limitada frente a las diferentes realidades socio-económicas locales.', 'es', 'The certification of organic products and fair trade enjoys great attention as a fundamental instrument for the introduction into global markets of environmental protection and social equity issues. However, consideration of a mechanism to register for the evaluation of the conformity of these aspects seems limited to various local socio-economic realities.', 'en', 'The certification of organic products and fair trade enjoys great attention as a fundamental instrument for the introduction into global markets of environmental protection and social equity issues. However, consideration of a mechanism to register for the evaluation of the conformity of these aspects seems limited to various local socio-economic realities.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-24', NULL),
