(2031, 4077, 'Aplicación del caolín como tratamiento fitosanitario en el cultivo ecológico del olivo en la comarca del priorat (Tarragona)', 'es', 'Application of kaolin as a phytosanitary treatment in the ecological cultivation of olive trees in the region of priorat (Tarragona)', 'en', 'Application of kaolin as a phytosanitary treatment in the ecological cultivation of olive trees in the region of priorat (Tarragona)', 89, 6, 2, '2014-01-24', NULL),
(2032, 4077, 'Se evalúa la eficacia del caolín [Al4Si4O10(OH)8] en la lucha contra la mosca del olivo (Bactrocera oleae), en agricultura ecológica. Los ensayos se realizaron en dos fincas de las comarcas del Priorat (Tarragona) y Les Garrigues (Lleida), los años 2004 y 2005, sobre 10 olivos y otros 10 testigos no tratados, de la variedad ‘Arbequina’ y según un diseño factorial simple.', 'es', 'Evaluates the effectiveness of [Al4Si4O10 (OH) 8] kaolin in the fight against the olive fly (Bactrocera oleae), in organic farming. Trials were conducted on two farms in the regions of Priorat (Tarragona) and Les Garrigues (Lleida), 2004 and 2005 on 10 olive trees and other 10 witnesses not treated, the variety ''Arbequina'' and according to a simple factorial design.', 'en', 'Evaluates the effectiveness of [Al4Si4O10 (OH) 8] kaolin in the fight against the olive fly (Bactrocera oleae), in organic farming. Trials were conducted on two farms in the regions of Priorat (Tarragona) and Les Garrigues (Lleida), 2004 and 2005 on 10 olive trees and other 10 witnesses not treated, the variety ''Arbequina'' and according to a simple factorial design.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-24', NULL),
