(2045, 4079, 'Durante el verano de 2004 se llevó a cabo una experiencia con patata cv Agria con el objetivo de estudiar el efecto del ozono troposférico sobre esta variedad. Se escogieron 3 localidades en la cuenca del río Turia (Villar del Arzobispo, Godelleta y Benifaió. Valencia) y una cuarta situada en la provincia de Sevilla.', 'es', 'During the summer of 2004 was conducted an experience with potato sour cv in order to study the effect of ozone tropospheric on this variety. You chose 3 locations in the basin of the River Turia (Villar del Arzobispo, Godelleta and Benifaio. Valencia) and a fourth in the province of Seville.', 'en', 'During the summer of 2004 was conducted an experience with potato sour cv in order to study the effect of ozone tropospheric on this variety. Three locations were chosen in the basin of the River Turia (Villar del Arzobispo, Godelleta and Benifaio. Valencia) and a fourth in the province of Seville.', 89, 8, 2, '2014-01-24', NULL),
